---
title: Lemon Oregano Chicken with Kumara, Spinach & Feta Toss
description: Simple, clean flavours are the highlight of this Mediterranean-inspired dish. This combination of vegetables is well loved by the Greeks, so you can trust that this simple side will hit the spot. Paired with fragrant oregano chicken, you'll only wish you were eating this dish by the sea in Santorini.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bb41bd2ae08b568d556f3c2-fc5de7a4.jpg
